description:
Hello, I'm Agatha and merry Christmas! 🎄

In today's video, I'm happy to share with you my top 6 my lips but better lipsticks that are very affordable 🥰 I hope my video helped you in some way 😊 if you do have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise) 

Products mentioned:
Detail Cosmetics Velvet Flush in BO - https://shopee.ph/Detail-Cosmetics-Velvet-Flush-in-Bo-i.10489673.7765431889

Detail Cosmetics Powder Pout in RAIZA CONTAWI - https://shopee.ph/Detail-Cosmetics-Powder-Pout-in-Raiza-Contawi-i.10489673.4355406279 

Squad Cosmetics Multi-Purpose Mousse Cream in BUBBLY - https://shopee.ph/Squad-Cosmetics-Multi-Purpose-Mousse-Cream-in-Bubbly-i.186309228.7737842878

Vice Co Good Vibes Lipstick in GANDERZ - https://shopee.ph/Vice-Co-Good-Vibes-Matte-Lipstick-Ganderz-3.5g-i.53860691.865066089

Vice Co x Anne Clutz Phenomenal Velvet Lipstick in BUDOL - https://shopee.ph/Anne-Clutz-Phenomenal-Velvet-Liquid-Lipstick-in-Budol-i.53860691.5056412546

Sunnies face lip dip in FEMMEBOT - https://shopee.ph/Sunnies-Face-Lip-Dip-in-Femmebot-i.109652002.2411986301
